high_descs: Walk around the counters in front of you, then along the left into the hall, taking the first right into the bedroom and going to the dresser to the left of the door you entered.
Pick up the knife from the dresser.
Turn around from the dresser and walk along the room to the other door on the left, entering the room ahead and stopping at the desk ahead.
Slice the loaf of bread on the desk.
Turn left and exit this room into the hallway, then turn left and go down all the way into the large room, going to the large dining table at the corner to the right.
Place the knife down on the table.
Return to the desk with the loaf of bread you sliced.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Go back to the area with the large dining table, then go to the kitchen in the area next to it, approaching the microwave at the corner of the counters.
Use the microwave on the slice of bread and pick it back up.
Go to the dining table you put the knife down on.
Place the bread down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread on a dining table.

high_descs: Turn left to the hall way and go to the first room on the right, go toward the dresser.
Pick up the butterknife on the dresser.
Go to the doorway between the dresser and nightstand,  go straight across to the wood dining table.
Slice the bread on the dining table with the white chair.
Turn left and go to the hallway, and go straight across to get to the dining table in the kitchen.
Place the butterknife on the diningtable in the top right corner.
Turn to the hallway beside the TV, go to the last room on the right and go to the desk with the white chair.
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Go straight across to the door, turn left and go to the end of the hall to reach the kitchen, head to the microwave.
Place the bread in the microwave, heat it, then pick it back up.
Turn around and go across to the dining table.
Place the bread on the diningtable in the top right corner across from the tea pot.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of Bread on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the kitchen counter to the hallway and turn right into the first room and go to the dresser.
Pick up the butterknife from the dresser.
Turn right and then exit out the door on the left and go to the bread on the brown table.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn left, exit the room, turn left and go to the end and then turn right to go to the diningtable.
Place the butterknife on the diningtable.
Turn back around and go down the hall to the second door on the right to the brown desk.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn around, exit the room, go left down the hall and back to the kitchen table with the knife and turn right to go to the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave, turn the microwave on and then pick up the bread.
Turn around and go to the diningtable.
Place the bread on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of warmed Bread on the DiningTable.
